Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.41,0:01:17.22,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}堅韌不撓的藤蔓的形狀
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.88,0:01:22.64,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}懷中藏有刺的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.11,0:01:29.62,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}各自懷著不可言喻的昨天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.62,0:01:33.37,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}向天空而去
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.77,0:01:38.83,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}只要生命還在  就喊出願望吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.14,0:01:44.33,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}心意終將貫穿星辰
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.55,0:01:49.62,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}在漫長又短暫的時間的盡頭
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.93,0:01:52.17,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}你生存過的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.07,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}證據會
